  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, one would think that with the physical liberation, this would more or less be the end of all the traumatic feelings, and all the anxieties, and all the worries.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, based on my own life experience, the-- this issue and, and, and its effect on people didn't end with liberation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think it has even ended today, because the need for us to do this interview itself shows that we still have-- dealing with a big, big problem here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And unfortunately, based on my perception of what's going on in this world, I think it will never, ever totally dissolve itself or go away as, as, as, as a crushing burden on whoever has a Jewish conscience.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, the incident that, that kind of led into the post-liberation-- I say not post-war, post-liberation because we were liberated in the fall because we were-- but other parts-- the war wasn't over.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war was only over, I would say, approximately six, seven months after we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- And so, so, so there's a difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, right after liberation, our liberation, there was the Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember very well-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know you asked about the incident in the park, but this is all part of our-- of what-- of, of, our-- our, our environment, the psychological make up right after the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
